# Bright & Beryl Jewelry E-Commerce Website

## Project Overview
This is a Next.js 14 jewelry e-commerce website built with React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS. The website showcases jewelry products including rings, necklaces, earrings, and bracelets.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 14 (App Router)
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **State Management**: React Context API (CartContext)

## Project Structure
```
app/
├── components/          # Reusable React components
│   ├── Navbar.tsx       # Navigation bar with cart counter
│   ├── Footer.tsx       # Footer with links and info
│   └── ProductCard.tsx  # Product display card
├── context/
│   └── CartContext.tsx  # Shopping cart state management
├── data/
│   └── products.ts      # Product data and types
├── shop/
│   └── page.tsx         # Shop/catalog page
├── cart/
│   └── page.tsx         # Shopping cart page
├── product/[id]/
│   └── page.tsx         # Product detail pages
├── about/
│   └── page.tsx         # About us page
├── layout.tsx           # Root layout with providers
├── page.tsx             # Homepage
└── globals.css          # Global styles
```

## Key Features
- Product browsing and filtering by category
- Shopping cart with session storage
- Product detail pages with image galleries
- Responsive design (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Indian Rupee (₹) pricing
- Product categories: New Launches, Featured Collections, Best Sellers, Pure Silver

## Coding Conventions
- Use TypeScript for type safety
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes for styling
- Use Lucide React for icons
- Product data structure includes: id, name, category, price, material, gemstone, images, featured, newLaunch, bestSeller, pureSilver, inStock, rating, reviews
- Prices are in Indian Rupees (₹) without decimals
- Use `toLocaleString('en-IN')` for Indian number formatting

## Important Notes
- Cart uses sessionStorage (clears when browser closes)
- Product images use Next.js Image component
- All prices are in Indian Rupees
- GST is 18% (Indian tax rate)
- Free shipping threshold: ₹40,000
- Brand name: "Bright & Beryl"

## Component Patterns
- Use 'use client' directive for client components
- Use Link from next/link for navigation
- Use Image from next/image for optimized images
- Product cards use ProductCard component
- Cart state managed via CartContext

## Styling Guidelines
- Primary colors: brown tones (primary-600, primary-700)
- Gold accent: gold-600, gold-700
- Use rounded-2xl for card corners
- Use font-serif for headings (Cormorant Garamond)
- Use font-sans for body text (Inter)

